collections.name: MATOI Series: Conceptual Wearables
collections.description:
"To wear is to embody, to adorn is to transform."

MATOI series redefines fashion as an art form, merging sculpture, digital aesthetics, and avant-garde couture. Inspired by MATOI (纏)—the act of draping and merging with one’s surroundings—each piece embodies fluidity, transformation, and impermanence.

Blending AI-generated design with sculptural fashion, this collection explores the boundary between body, material, and space, shaping the future of wearable art.

collections.name: Celestial Rites: The Alchemy of the Divine
collections.description:
Celestial Rites: The Alchemy of the Divine" is a mesmerizing collection that explores the fusion of myth, mysticism, and cosmic transcendence. Each artwork serves as a gateway to an ethereal dimension, where celestial priestesses, enigmatic deities, and alchemical symbols converge to depict the eternal dance between creation and destruction, light and shadow, spirit and matter.

Rich with sacred geometry, astral sigils, and ritualistic altars, this collection draws inspiration from ancient mythologies, esoteric traditions, and the boundless mysteries of the universe. Each piece is imbued with profound symbolism—portraying figures suspended between the earthly and the divine, engaged in a timeless journey of enlightenment.
Perfect for collectors who seek art that transcends the mundane, "Celestial Rites" offers a glimpse into the hidden mechanics of the cosmos, inviting viewers to decipher the secrets woven into its celestial tapestry.

collections.description:
Je suis Virginie Gérôme, une créatrice passionnée explorant les possibilités infinies de l'art numérique.Je m'inspire de la nature, la technologie, pour créer des compositions uniques captivant l'imagination.
Je travaille principalement avec l'art génératif. et la photographie Mon objectif est d’exprimer des émotions, provoquer la réflexion, repousser les limites de l'art numérique.
Je suis passionnée par l'évolution de l'art numérique et je cherche à repousser les frontières de la créativité à travers mes projets. Découvrez mon univers artistique et merci pour votre intérêt !
